Prevent user from deleting notes.
 
    db.users.updateOne({ email: "demo" }, { $set: { 'claims.canDeleteNotes': false } } )


Delete user.

    db.users.remove({ email: "demo" }, true)


Open mongo console from command line.

    Write 'mongo' in new terminal window.


Show databases/collections.

    show dbs
    show collections


Switch to database.

    use {db name}


Show collection.

    db.{collection name}.find()